<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Dashboard Cliente</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: #f6f8fc;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 750px;
      width: 100%;
      background: white;
      padding: 2rem 3rem;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(110, 193, 228, 0.3);
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0f75bc;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .welcome-text {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #0f75bc;
      margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .promo-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-style: italic;
      background: #dff3ff;
      border-left: 6px solid #6ec1e4;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.7rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      user-select: none;
    }

    p.accion-text {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0f75bc;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .main-buttons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .main-buttons a button {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6ec1e4 60%, #f9a826 100%);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.45rem 1.3rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(110, 193, 228, 0.6);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      min-width: 140px;
    }

    .main-buttons a button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f9a826 60%, #6ec1e4 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(249, 168, 38, 0.7);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: #6ec1e4;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #6ec1e4;
      padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
      width: max-content;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .vet-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1.1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .vet-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(110, 193, 228, 0.3);
      padding: 1rem 1.4rem;
      width: 220px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .vet-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(249, 168, 38, 0.5);
    }

    .vet-card h4 {
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
      color: #0f75bc;
    }

    .vet-card button {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6ec1e4 60%, #f9a826 100%);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .vet-card button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f9a826 60%, #6ec1e4 100%);
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    p.no-vets {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>¡Hola, <%= user.nombre %>!</h1>
    <div class="welcome-text">¡Qué bueno verte por aquí!</div>

    <div class="promo-text">
      En nuestra veterinaria, tu mascota recibe la atención profesional que merece, con especialistas dedicados y un trato lleno de cariño. Estamos aquí para cuidar la salud y felicidad de tu mejor amigo peludo.
    </div>

    <p class="accion-text">¿Qué deseas hacer hoy?</p>

    <div class="main-buttons">
      <a href="/citas/agendar"><button>Agendar nueva cita</button></a>
      <a href="/citas/mis-citas"><button>Ver mis citas</button></a>
    </div>

    <h3>Comunícate en tiempo real con los especialistas que cuidan a tu mascota</h3>

    <div class="vet-list">
      <% if (typeof veterinarios !== 'undefined' && veterinarios.length > 0) { %>
        <% veterinarios.forEach(vet => { %>
          <div class="vet-card">
            <h4><%= vet.nombre %></h4>
            <a href="/chat/cliente/<%= vet.id %>">
              <button>Iniciar chat</button>
            </a>
          </div>
        <% }) %>
      <% } else { %>
        <p class="no-vets">No hay veterinarios disponibles en este momento.</p>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
